        "input": "[if(endsWith(parameters('privateDnsZoneIds')[copyIndex('blobDnsZoneIds')], format('/privatelink.blob{0}', variables('blobEndpoint'))), parameters('privateDnsZoneIds')[copyIndex('blobDnsZoneIds')], null())]"
